Updated January 1 , 2013
In connection with a restructuring of our business , we have updated our Privacy Policy to reflect that the Site is operated by Zapppos IP , Inc. ( successor-in-interest to Zappos Development , Inc. ) .
Although the substance of the policy is effectively the same as in the past , there are some changes .
For example , The updated policy no longer refers to the Free Clothing Giveaway as it is not currently offered on our website .
The updated policy now refers to contests and sweepstakes , as we may offer either or both on our website from time to time .
The updated policy allows information to be shared among Zappos.com , Inc. and the affiliates it controls .
These are only a few of the changes to the policy , and this brief summary should not affect your interpretation of it .
Please read the Privacy Policy carefully .
Your continued use of the website constitutes your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy .
